{"tid":2273902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加強控制東海「中國管轄海域」執法  華授權海警動武 日漁船恐被針對","createTime":"2020-11-06T05:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T06:17:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c84a09dd7c8dbf785a34ebd056ec1eda3e788f","tid":2273902,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:31:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201106/OOXQINTD3FA27GDVCHZ45JX774/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201106%2FOOXQINTD3FA27GDVCHZ45JX774%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8h3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=6ca01606\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201106%2FOOXQINTD3FA27GDVCHZ45JX774%2F&h=330c7166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201106/OOXQINTD3FA27GDVCHZ45JX774/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n加強控制東海「中國管轄海域」執法 <br />\n華授權海警動武 日漁船恐被針對<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WxjyYADqlGQ6LyGpKFfLuVmevsU=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NL7WMZDXIZE4LHHVYSIFOB223Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWxjyYADqlGQ6LyGpKFfLuVmevsU%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNL7WMZDXIZE4LHHVYSIFOB223Q.jpg&h=847516af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地海警法草案允許海警可向拒檢外國船隻使用武器。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n解放軍近期加強在東海和南海的活動之際，全國人大常委會前日公佈《海警法》草案全文，明文規定海警機構對非法進入中國管轄海域的外國船舶，有權採取扣留和強制驅離等措施，並可在對方拒絕接受檢查時使用手持武器。日本傳媒高度關注中方此項立法，指在釣魚島（日稱尖閣諸島）周邊海域作業的日本漁船恐成針對對象。<br />\n<br />\n上月中旬在北京舉行的人大常委會會議，審議由中央軍事委員會提請審議的《海警法》草案，武警部隊司令員王寧受中央軍委。。。。。。。。。。。重大戰略部署。草案即日起進行一個月的公眾諮詢，預計將在下月舉行的人大常委會會議通過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DSQeQSvoVx-4caEy-BkdbCvYDDE=/664x618/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HRGBP7TMFZDQZEHPZIXYJSE3IA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDSQeQSvoVx-4caEy-BkdbCvYDDE%3D%2F664x618%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHRGBP7TMFZDQZEHPZIXYJSE3IA.gif&h=eda151f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可扣留及驅離外國船隻<br />\n<br />\n草案分11章合共80條，列明隸屬武警部隊的中國海警局，統一履行海上維權執法職責，包括在中國管轄海域開展巡航、警戒，值守重點島礁，排除危害國家主權、安全和海洋權益的行為，查處海上違反出境入境管理法律、走私、非法捕魚等行為。海警機構有權依法對在中國管轄海域航行、停泊、作業的外國船泊進行識別查證，對有違法嫌疑者可以跟蹤監視，並有權責令非法進入中國內海、領海的外國船舶採取扣留、強制驅離或拖離等措施。<br />\n<br />\n此外，草案列明「國家主權、主權權利和管轄權在海上正在受到外國組織、個人的不法侵害或者面臨不法侵害的緊迫危險時」，海警機構。。。。。。。。。。。。若受到武器攻擊時還可以使用艦載或機載武器。最後，草案明確海警機構依照中央軍委的「執行防衞作戰等任務」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連續57日駛近日領海外側<br />\n<br />\n日本《產經新聞》昨報道稱，中國海警局近期「在東海尖閣諸島周邊透過巡邏船反覆侵入（日本）領海之際，在周邊作業的日本漁船恐怕成為遭針對對象。」日本共同社日前指，海上保安廳巡邏船發現中國海警局四艘船隻周一（2日）在該海域附近的日本領海外側毗連區航行，引述當局指中國公務船已連續57天在該海域出現，全年累計已達283天，刷新歷史最高紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n日本官房長官加藤勝信昨在記者會回應中國《海警法》立法時稱，日。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大網/ 日本《產經新聞》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XBSl4Sb0Hb9XS394X507TCCOYx8=/411x863/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WC2FMIHJKJAQRLANGC7II3XX2I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXBSl4Sb0Hb9XS394X507TCCOYx8%3D%2F411x863%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWC2FMIHJKJAQRLANGC7II3XX2I.gif&h=93fdae4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af279b4121e5cfbd7878123387b206c26c3e7592","tid":2273902,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"周邊國家都整條見到支那漁船就開火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965d8494e8d32df4f423cf5d29a16c073fb425a1","tid":2273902,"uid":152222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:38:50.000Z","msg":"見拜登選情好，支共即刻出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cec10deef82fa5957d813ddd007ea187e3eedf0","tid":2273902,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />南海都未搞掂<br />\n<br />\n就玩埋東海"},{"pid":"653dacff57b6c43a46f37d220333b511223d35ac","tid":2273902,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"965d8494e8d32df4f423cf5d29a16c073fb425a1","tid":2273902,"uid":152222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:38:50.000Z","msg":"見拜登選情好，支共即刻出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:17:24.000Z","msg":"應該係趁美國內亂<br />\n同埋拜登都係奶支"}]}